    <title>记乌俄战争</title>
    <link href="https://innofox.me/ji-wu-e-zhan-zheng.html"/>
    <id>https://innofox.me/ji-wu-e-zhan-zheng.html</id>
    <published>2022-03-01T00:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-03-02T04:13:33.044Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="乌俄战争与国内舆论记"><a href="#乌俄战争与国内舆论记" class="headerlink" title="乌俄战争与国内舆论记"></a>乌俄战争与国内舆论记</h1><blockquote><p>杀人者在毁坏世界，救人者在修补它，而炮灰资格的诸公，却在恭维杀人者。</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>俄Putin入侵乌克兰。微博一片叫好，甚至“收留漂亮乌克兰美女”之言论。</p><h2 id="拿破仑与隋那-–鲁迅"><a href="#拿破仑与隋那-–鲁迅" class="headerlink" title="拿破仑与隋那 –鲁迅"></a>拿破仑与隋那 –鲁迅</h2><blockquote><p>集：且介亭杂文</p></blockquote><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/innotsufox/static-src/main/img/202203012327914.jpg" style="zoom:50%;" /><h2 id="并引正义网友言论"><a href="#并引正义网友言论" class="headerlink" title="并引正义网友言论"></a>并引正义网友言论</h2><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/innotsufox/static-src/main/img/202203012333566.jpg" style="zoom:50%;" /><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/innotsufox/static-src/main/img/202203012339657.jpg" style="zoom:50%;" /><h2 id="结"><a href="#结" class="headerlink" title="结"></a>结</h2><p>国内许多人已然成为被国家机器洗脑的傀儡，并逐渐nazi化。</p><p><strong><em>纳粹：纳之精粹，我是不想使用如此亲希特拉的词</em></strong></p><p>记于二零二二年三月一日</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
    
